episodes.title: 1st Amendment Audit(UK), Scientology Saint Hill Manor QUESTIONS & ANSWERS
episodes.description:
In this edition of Life On The Beat w/ Nasty Nathanial I find myself back in the United Kingdom where I am teaming up with UK auditor @flukedog . Together we are taking a look at Saint Hill Manor. This property serves as the Church Of Scientology's headquarters for the United Kingdom. But will the staff, security, and parishioners respect our rights under UK law to take photos and video from a public space? You'll just have to watch and see. 

PLEASE NOTE: This video is for educational and training purposes and contains news worthy content meant to educate the public.
